data.description: A neighborhood that feels exclusive and a home with vaulted 11-foot-high ceilings will ‘WOW’ guests as they come through the foyer. Living room skylights offer amazing bursts of natural light during the day and dazzling dashes of stars at night. A spacious dining room ready to seat your family for the holidays and special occasions all year long. The over-sized living room is the perfect place for gathering in the winter, while the big backyard is the best place to celebrate the summer. Three bedrooms, two full baths, and a main-floor laundry make the full-sized walk-out basement a dedicated area for storage and recreation. The attached garage makes getting the groceries inside easy, no matter what the weather. This home is listed AS-IS. All inspections will be for the buyer’s information only. Seller will not make any repairs or offer any credit towards closing. A genuine gem here, priced to sell fast!
